## SymbolMetadata.enumType property

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

Whether this enum or string literal union type is open or closed for exhaustive consumption. - 'open': New members may be added at any time; consumers should handle unknown values - 'closed': Intended to be consumed exhaustively; adding a member is breaking - undefined: Unmarked, defaults to 'closed' behavior

**Signature:**

```typescript
enumType?: 'open' | 'closed';
```
